To conclude, talent connector is basically an application which helps to find out talented people who have potential to do extra 
ordinary things but sometimes are not able to do so due to no proper guidance or resources so, the idea is to find out the individuals 
and collect them on a platform where they can interact with those people who are expert in the field in which these people seek for guidance.
There will be basically two types of users of the application one who are expert in some field and the other who needs the opinion of these experts
to do more in their respective field. This platform tries to polish the skills of individual by providing them proper guidance of people who already have 
done much in such field their experiences make people polished and motivate them to do hard work so that in future they make their name and serve the mankind. 
The application will have easy to use interface which the user can interact with. It will have a proper check and balanced environment in which one can feel free
to ask question to the experts and the experts will provide them with proper answers.
So, in short by talent connector really can connect a common individual with a world famous personality.

